				<wikidot:authorName>Leveritas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1558990</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>The item activates 12 seconds after Subject A and Subject B enter its area of influence. Item proceeds to engage with Subject A in a drawing contest. Papers and crayons are provided.</p> </blockquote> <p>How does the SCP communicate to the staff that it wants to engage in a drawing contest if paper and crayons are provided afterwards?</p> <p>Apart from that, good job!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
